{"tid":1872761,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"「黑警等天收」「黑警有報應」 係無用架，淨化Facebook行動 每日一更","createTime":"2020-02-10T08:52:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-10T11:33:04.000Z","uid":89974,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0ab6f1c09185ec70c2bd42edbf48d8063ac46fc4","tid":1872761,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T08:52:49.000Z","msg":"「黑警等天收」「黑警有報應」<br />\n<br />\nFb好多呢種留句言就當做咗野嘅人，以蘋果/立場新聞及眾多群組為甚。<br />\n<br />\n雖然係同路人，但呢種心態其實係極懦弱同完全被動，我地唔可以令呢種風氣係示威者入面蔓延，否則個個都變哂等運到。<br />\n<br />\n我地應該鼓勵示威者更加進取咁行動，所以現正呼籲所有連登巴絲，舉行由<span style=\"color: blue;\">今日起直到下星期日</span>嘅Facebook 淨化活動。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n行動</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n目標：<span style=\"color: purple;\">蘋果，立場</span>所有的post<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><br />\n1.每一次你見到有人留言「黑警死全家」「黑警等天收」「黑警有報應」等回應時，用以下template回應佢(留意唔好短時間番太多次，會俾FB當係spam，想自己改下字眼都得)：</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;template&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;</span><br />\n好人不長命，禍害遺千年，剩係靠許願係令唔到黑警暴斃，但我地一齊合力係可以架。<br />\n你可唔可以應承我同我一齊做以下至少一樣野？<br />\n<br />\n罷工 （要脅政府）<br />\n罷稅（斷狗糧）<br />\n杯葛黑警，斷絕社會關係<br />\n參加每一次黃陣營舉辦嘅活動，官方/非官方都去<br />\n杯葛藍絲，斷絕社會關係<br />\n有口罩俾手足唔好俾廢老藍絲<br />\n每日盡量去法院聲援被捕手足<br />\n每日發文宣俾朋友<br />\n試用Twitter<br />\n出街時貼memo紙係街邊做流動文宣<br />\n金錢支援手足<br />\n捐錢俾612<br />\n<br />\n杯葛藍店支持黃店（hktvmall 取代惠康華潤，唔食大家樂元氣）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果你認同我地的話，下次見到有其他人留黑警死全家等回應時，請複製貼上此回覆！<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;template&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">2.如果覺得template太長，可以用呢張代替</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fBfK9Fd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfBfK9Fd.jpg&h=a3b97eda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><br />\n3.每見到一個合資格嘅人選都留言一次，如果有人已經留咁嘅話就用like推佢前啲</span>"},{"pid":"37a1b1395ad48863ca6d72ea200c0485958af408","tid":1872761,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T08:53:41.000Z","msg":"延伸閱讀：<br />\n<br />\n突發開花只會係咁犧牲最有行動力個班手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1870672/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1870672/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n支援醫護罷工，馬上加入先行者罷工隊！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1867345\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1867345</a><br />\n<br />\n睇完勇武目前嘅瓶頸位你就知道點解今次罷工要贏盡佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1862193\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1862193</a><br />\n<br />\n[討論檢討]好多搞手搞活動都係大伏<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1865401\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1865401</a><br />\n<br />\n痴撚線，疫病打到嚟仲要手足搞黎明行動？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1846732\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1846732</a><br />\n<br />\n得罪講句，呢個禮拜仲番緊工嘅就唔好跳出嚟話醫護廢啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1867936\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1867936</a>"},{"pid":"b6778f30da9a16a8d7f88e222a238c3ebae63f05","tid":1872761,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T08:53:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d130d5727094e1f306fbdd36102f264c934be032","tid":1872761,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T08:54:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"211262648401c92e98bef6590f3a48331722d753","tid":1872761,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T08:54:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47b02ab8fe7e545223f035ad5557db2fc9167db5","tid":1872761,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T08:54:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"